snippet.title: ML on Raspberry Pi with MediaPipe
snippet.description:
Get started with Google's on-device machine learning tool, MediaPipe, and learn how you can integrate it into your MediaPipe apps. 

Find tutorials on how to create ML models, implement common ML tasks, such as hand gesture recognition, audio classification, and text similarity in MediaPipe apps, and more!

snippet.title: 2023 Solution Challenge Demo Day
snippet.description:
Check out the 2023 Solution Challenge Demo Day hosted by Google Developer Student Clubs (GDSC). Don't miss the opportunity to watch the top 10 finalists demo their projects supporting the UN Sustainable Development Goals and celebrate the Top 3 winning teams!

Learn more about Google Developer Student Clubs by visiting https://goo.gle/gdsc
